Diversity Output from Input File:  SI_78-79_0-2m  (June 10, 2022)
NOTE:  Chao's estimated CV for Incidence distribution = 0.608. Because the CV > 0.5, Anne Chao recommends
that you re-compute Chao2 using the Classic instead of the Bias-Corrected option in the Diversity Settings screen.
Then, based on the results with the Classic option, report the larger of Chao2 and ICE as the better estimate for incidence-based richness.
